0:
”Alexa, ask Chicago Beaches what is the temperature at Ohio Street Beach”
”Alexa, ask Chicago Beaches is Howard Beach safe”
”Alexa, ask Chicago Beaches how cold is Rainbow Beach”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: chicago beaches
des:
Queries Chicago Beach Data for automatic water sensor data. Gives temperature or water safety readings for any sensor that is currently online and giving data including the following beaches:

Montrose Beach*
Ohio Street Beach*
Calumet Beach*
Osterman Beach*
Rainbow Beach*
Margaret T Burroughs Beach
South Shore Beach
Leone Beach
Marion Mahony Griffin Beach
Humboldt Beach
Foster Beach
Rogers Beach
Hartigan Beach
Oak Street Beach
Howard Beach
Oakwood Beach

Only those names marked with an asterisk will give you temperature readings. You must say the full name of the beach to work properly. If available (sensors may often be offline or unavailable), the most recent water temperature reading in Fahrenheit will be given to you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
